<h2>Making connections one meetup at a time</h2>

<div class="how-it-works-button">
  <button>How it works</button>
</div>

<div class="how-it-works-content">
  <div class="how-it-works-description col-md-4 col-md-offset-4">
    By looking at the meetups you've gone to in the past, your current
    location, as well as the availability listed on your Google Calendar,
    we're able to provide you better recommendations via our website,
    text messaging, and/or email.
  </div>
  <div class="row images">
      <div class="col-md-5 meetup"><%= image_tag "denver_rb.jpeg" %></div>
      <div class="col-md-2 plus"><%= image_tag "plus.jpeg" %></div>
      <div class="col-md-5 map"><%= image_tag "denver.jpeg" %></div>
  </div>
</div>

<h3>Helping you to connect</h3>

<div class="login">
  <button><%= link_to "Sign up with Meetup", "/auth/meetup" %></button>
</div>

